## Introduction to App Lab

##### The Creating Apps for Devices unit begins with a lesson on App Lab to get your students familiar with the tool they will use this unit. If your students are already familiar with App Lab, you may decide to skip this lesson. <a href="https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/115001479372-How-can-I-hide-certain-units-or-lessons-from-my-students" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click here</a> to learn more about skipping this lesson, allowing your classes to start right away with Chapter 1: Inputs and Outputs.


